data.text:
Andrew Lane (who also writes as Andy Lane) is the author of the Young Sherlock Holmes series of novels.

Lane is an author and journalist, also know for writing spin-off novels for Doctor Who, one of which included a crossover with Sherlock Holmes and Doctor Watson.
